title: Grateful Dead Live at Jai-Alai Fronton on 1974-06-23
description:
Set I
Ramble On Rose
Black Throated Wind
Mississippi Half-Step Uptown Toodleloo
Beat It On Down The Line
Row Jimmy
Jack Straw
Let It Rock
Cumberland Blues
El Paso
To Lay Me Down
Weather Report Suite >
Let It Grow >
China Doll
Set II
Ship Of Fools
Big River
Black Peter
Around & Around
Dark Star >
Spanish Jam >
U.S. Blues
Uncle John's Band >
One More Saturday Night
Casey Jones


Comment
Phil & Ned Jam between sets

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Donna Jean Godchaux - Vocals

reviews.review_text:
Maybe one of the best Audience recordings ever Nice sounding transfer of this classic recording.

If you haven't heard this show yet, what are you waiting for?
